    def: 'Relevant to root urban regeneration not in blank slates, but in the profound, subjective histories and place identities already held by the local inhabitants. — A curated collection of oral histories, personal stories, and emotional mappings that translate the intangible cultural memory of a community into a tangible planning asset.',
