    def: 'Relevant to move beyond visual aesthetics and capture how the city is actually heard, smelled, and physically felt by human bodies to guide more holistic urban design. — Multisensory maps and datasets detailing the acoustic quality (soundscapes), olfactory environment (smellscapes), and emotional responses attached to specific urban zones.',
