    def: 'Relevant to mathematically measure the extent to which urban geometry exacerbates heat islands, establishing a scientific baseline for thermal comfort before designing climate adaptation interventions. — Calculations and thermal mappings quantifying the proportion of sky visible from a specific point, proving how street canyons trap heat and dictating whe…',
