    def: 'Relevant to safely test new, temporary legal rules and shared-management structures in a controlled environment before scaling them into permanent city-wide laws,. — A tested, temporary governance or financial arrangement (e.g., a collaborative pact or a specialized testing domain) evaluated in practice to observe outcomes and mitigate risks before instit…',
